column5: WELL STILL NO CAM. WIFE REFUSES TO GIVE IT BACK UNTIL TRIP PICS ARE OFF IT LOL HAD PUPPY DUTIES THE LAST 2 DAYS SO LAST MIN I SNUCK OUT THIS MORN. SUN UP WATER WAS REAL SLUSHY. HAD TO PITCH BETWEEN THE ICE LIKE LILYPADS LOL ENDED UP GETTIN SIX BOWS AND 3 BROWNS. 30KM WINDS KICKED IN JUST AFTER SUNRISE . COLD BUT WORTH THE OUTING. NOW IM GETTIN MY CAM BACK FOR NEXT WEEK  LOL JUST HOPE IT DONT SNOW NOW OR ILL HAVE TO PLOW
LOL   Nice going Scott.  I take it you took advantage of Phils offer.
